<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Smart Wijesekara — exact spec
  Gaps = 0dp in XML; visual spacing done in MyKeyboardView (innerPad=2.2dp each side)
  All shift chars handled in MyInputMethodService.wijShiftMap

  Number row (12 keys): 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 0 - =
  Row 1 (10 keys): Q(ු) W(අ) E(ැ) R(ර) T(එ) Y(හ) U(ම) I(ස) O(ද) P(ච)
  Row 2 (10 keys): A(්) S(ි) D(ා) F(ෙ) G(ට) H(ය) J(ව) K(න) L(ක) ;(ත)
